leave

Class LeaveRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • leave.LeaveRequest

  • public class LeaveRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    The LeaveRequest class represents a leave request submitted by a user. It contains details such as the request ID, requester ID, leave date, reason for the leave, and the current status of the request.
